&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate pipeline management and contribute to forecasting efforts to ensure goal alignment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer Engagement and Consultation:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
